WEBVTT

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:30.719
Old Master Chen,

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:33.239
If you want to get back at me,

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:34.760
I can understand that.

00:01:35.239 --> 00:01:35.879
But you shouldn't

00:01:35.879 --> 00:01:37.560
team up with that bastard Gu Zhantian!

00:01:38.239 --> 00:01:39.439
He's up to no good,

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:41.120
trying to swallow the Four Great Families of Haicheng.

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:42.879
Aren't you just hurting yourself by helping him?

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:43.920
Is that so?

00:01:44.519 --> 00:01:46.840
I'm short selling Qianfeng Group right now.

00:01:47.079 --> 00:01:48.239
In just a few hours,

00:01:48.239 --> 00:01:49.439
I've already made...

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:51.079
How much was it?

00:01:51.439 --> 00:01:52.280
About...

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:54.640
Eight billion.

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:56.239
Oh.

00:01:56.879 --> 00:01:58.439
How could I make so much?

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:00.519
Which idiot

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:03.079
is trying to save Qianfeng?

00:02:04.359 --> 00:02:05.159
Old Master Chen,

00:02:05.719 --> 00:02:06.840
you made your money,

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:08.159
so why do you have to insult people?

00:02:09.479 --> 00:02:10.120
If Gu Zhantian

00:02:10.120 --> 00:02:11.360
really swallows Qianfeng,

00:02:11.479 --> 00:02:12.439
the next one

00:02:12.439 --> 00:02:13.439
will be the Chen Family.

00:02:13.439 --> 00:02:14.879
You think I don't know that?

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:16.080
But right now,

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.120
do you have the capital to fight him?

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.000
With you

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.319
throwing money in like this,

00:02:21.479 --> 00:02:22.400
can your capital chain

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:24.039
last for three days?

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.639
If the Chen Family could also...

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.159
We can't.

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:35.719
Mengyun.

00:02:35.719 --> 00:02:36.639
What are you...

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:37.919
Grandpa,

00:02:38.479 --> 00:02:40.319
do you have the heart to let your great-grandson

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:42.759
be born to a father running from debts?

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:45.080
Mengyun,

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:45.919
you don't have to...

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:47.840
Between you and me,

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:49.240
there's no need to say more.

00:02:51.479 --> 00:02:52.759
All your scheming

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:56.240
is just used to screw over our Chen Family, huh?

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:57.840
Mengyun,

00:02:58.479 --> 00:03:00.479
it's not that Grandpa won't help him.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:02.960
It's that the Chen Family's capital chain

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.719
really can't hold up anymore.

00:03:04.759 --> 00:03:06.240
This battle

00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:07.759
is all about capital.

00:03:08.039 --> 00:03:09.639
If this kid wants to win,

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:11.439
he'll need heaven's help.

00:03:17.639 --> 00:03:18.479
What?

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:19.479
Really?

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:21.759
Mr. Lu!

00:03:21.759 --> 00:03:22.560
Look!

00:03:22.639 --> 00:03:23.560
It's going up!

00:03:23.719 --> 00:03:24.919
The stock prices of the Four Great Families

00:03:24.919 --> 00:03:25.759
are suddenly skyrocketing!

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:28.240
Our capital pool just gained tens of billions!

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.039
Dongfang Group is losing ground fast!

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:30.879
What?

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:34.080
Hahaha!

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:34.960
Old Master Chen,

00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:36.439
what were you just saying?

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:37.159
Hahaha!

00:03:37.159 --> 00:03:38.319
Consider yourself lucky, kid.

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:39.680
Heaven is helping me!

00:03:40.039 --> 00:03:40.840
Heaven is helping me!

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:41.639
No,

00:03:41.639 --> 00:03:42.439
what's going on?

00:03:44.639 --> 00:03:45.479
Fine.

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.479
I'd like to see

00:03:47.479 --> 00:03:49.840
who the real chosen one is.

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:55.159
That's more like it.

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:57.080
Hurry up and sign it.

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:58.240
Let me tell you,

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:00.080
the Leng Family is just the beginning.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:02.599
The Four Great Families of Haicheng

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:04.680
will all be in my pocket.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:17.720
I'm not signing.

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:19.360
What?

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:21.720
Still putting up a dying struggle?

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:23.439
Who's dying

00:04:23.439 --> 00:04:24.879
is still uncertain.

00:04:39.839 --> 00:04:41.959
Dasheng Group's stock price is skyrocketing

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:44.319
because I spearheaded

00:04:44.319 --> 00:04:45.720
the restart of the Chengnan project.

00:04:46.879 --> 00:04:47.680
Exactly.

00:04:47.759 --> 00:04:48.759
President Zhao said

00:04:48.759 --> 00:04:50.959
our Dasheng Group is a conscientious enterprise

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:52.759
that has made huge contributions to the city.

00:04:53.439 --> 00:04:54.639
They discussed it

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:55.439
and plan

00:04:55.439 --> 00:04:57.279
to cut our membership fees in half.

00:04:57.439 --> 00:04:58.879
They also approved a piece of

00:04:58.879 --> 00:04:59.879
discounted,

00:04:59.879 --> 00:05:01.279
super-potential land for us.

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:02.439
Just that

00:05:02.439 --> 00:05:03.959
wouldn't make it surge this fiercely, right?

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:05.360
Is there more?

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:06.680
The higher-ups also said

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:09.920
that once our Chengnan district is completed,

00:05:10.079 --> 00:05:10.879
they plan

00:05:10.879 --> 00:05:12.439
to hand over the development

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.160
of forty percent of the commercial zone

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.360
for us to manage.

00:05:15.439 --> 00:05:16.839
Our external cooperation hotline

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:17.920
has been ringing off the hook.

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:18.680
My grandpa's side

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:20.079
has also turned their guns around

00:05:20.439 --> 00:05:22.079
to strike hard at Gu Zhantian's side.

00:05:22.079 --> 00:05:23.240
Regarding Dongfang Group's business,

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:24.680
they also reported Gu Zhantian's side

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:26.079
for malicious acquisition.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:28.120
They are already under investigation.

00:05:28.120 --> 00:05:29.120
We no longer have to worry

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.480
about them targeting Qianfeng Group.

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:32.879
Chengwen,

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:34.680
when I took you to Qianfeng Group last time,

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:37.079
the thing you promised me...

00:05:37.079 --> 00:05:38.040
don't forget it.

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:41.480
Mengyun,

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.120
please, please.

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:44.920
Whatever you wanted to do,

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:46.839
when have I ever not supported you?

00:05:47.240 --> 00:05:48.680
However,

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:49.680
I have a condition.

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:53.360
What did you promise?

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.040
Since I was little,

00:06:14.040 --> 00:06:15.839
my family wouldn't let me do this

00:06:15.879 --> 00:06:17.360
or let me do that.

00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:20.120
So,

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:21.839
my biggest wish all along

00:06:22.439 --> 00:06:23.600
is to take the person I love

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:24.439
and let loose.

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:30.360
Mengyun,

00:06:30.439 --> 00:06:31.800
tell me,

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:33.560
will Gu Zhantian have a backup plan?

00:06:33.839 --> 00:06:34.439
Will those three

00:06:34.439 --> 00:06:35.439
be in danger?

00:06:36.439 --> 00:06:37.240
Chengwen,

00:06:37.879 --> 00:06:39.879
you can't mention other women here.

00:06:41.839 --> 00:06:42.639
Okay.

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:57.680
Sir,

00:06:58.839 --> 00:07:00.160
want a coconut?

00:07:02.439 --> 00:07:03.240
You...

00:07:07.040 --> 00:07:07.839
Sir,

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:09.720
how about a massage?

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:12.879
You'll get heatstroke in this sun.

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:15.160
Why are you guys here?

00:07:15.439 --> 00:07:16.560
The people I love

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:17.759
also include the sisters

00:07:17.759 --> 00:07:19.240
who fought alongside me recently.

00:07:19.279 --> 00:07:20.079
Is that not okay?

00:07:24.079 --> 00:07:24.879
Mengyun,

00:07:25.079 --> 00:07:26.240
you're so generous.

00:07:43.079 --> 00:07:43.959
Let me take a look.

00:07:44.079 --> 00:07:45.040
How did the pictures turn out?

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:52.279
Okay, okay, okay.

00:08:01.079 --> 00:08:01.480
Okay, okay.

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:11.319
Hahaha.

00:08:11.319 --> 00:08:12.240
Don't run!

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.439
Hahaha.

00:08:13.439 --> 00:08:13.920
Come here!

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:19.759
Ahahaha.

00:08:19.879 --> 00:08:21.920
Ahahaha.

00:08:21.920 --> 00:08:23.040
Where can you hide?

00:08:23.519 --> 00:08:24.319
Hahaha.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:27.519
Hahaha.

00:08:29.279 --> 00:08:29.680
Don't run!

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:30.439
I surrender, I surrender!

00:08:30.439 --> 00:08:31.480
Where are you going to hide?

00:08:31.959 --> 00:08:32.720
President Leng.

00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:35.559
Hahaha.

00:08:35.559 --> 00:08:36.360
Hurry, let's go!

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.440
Hahaha.

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:39.240
Run!

00:08:39.240 --> 00:08:39.759
Come on!

00:08:39.759 --> 00:08:42.320
Hahaha.

00:08:44.080 --> 00:08:47.440
Hahaha.

00:08:49.960 --> 00:08:51.039
Hahaha.

00:08:51.039 --> 00:08:51.440
Come on!

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:52.240
Cut it out!

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:55.279
Hahaha.

00:08:56.639 --> 00:08:57.519
Hit him, quick!

00:08:57.679 --> 00:08:59.440
Ahahaha.

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.120
Don't hide!

00:09:01.679 --> 00:09:02.360
Don't you run!

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:02.840
Don't run!

00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:03.159
Mr. Lu.

00:09:03.159 --> 00:09:03.759
Wait for me!

00:09:03.759 --> 00:09:04.559
Hahaha.

00:09:07.639 --> 00:09:08.720
These past few days,

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:09.919
everyone has been pretty tired.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.279
Alright.

00:09:11.519 --> 00:09:12.240
Everyone,

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:13.279
go back and get some rest.

00:09:14.080 --> 00:09:15.039
We're not going back.

00:09:15.039 --> 00:09:16.240
We're staying here with you.

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:17.440
I see

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.639
there are four rooms in total.

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:20.279
The four of us will take one room each.

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:21.360
You'll share a room with me.

00:09:21.840 --> 00:09:22.679
Sister Mengyun,

00:09:22.919 --> 00:09:24.679
even though you arranged everything today,

00:09:24.759 --> 00:09:25.840
and we had a lot of fun,

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.919
I still won't give Brother Chengwen up to you.

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:30.440
Brother Chengwen,

00:09:30.679 --> 00:09:31.519
today I brought

00:09:31.519 --> 00:09:33.279
a full JK uniform set,

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:35.080
and thick silver needles.

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:37.639
If you don't stay in my room,

00:09:37.639 --> 00:09:38.440
I can't guarantee my silver needles

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.879
won't end up poking you.

00:09:40.519 --> 00:09:41.320
Brother Chengwen,

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:42.639
these past few days,

00:09:42.639 --> 00:09:44.440
you should be very clear about my feelings.

00:09:45.080 --> 00:09:45.960
However,

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:47.679
sharing a boyfriend with others...

00:09:47.679 --> 00:09:48.440
that kind of thing,

00:09:48.639 --> 00:09:49.840
I just can't do it.

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:52.120
So tonight,

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:53.440
you must make a choice.

00:09:55.879 --> 00:09:57.960
What do you mean, sharing a boyfriend?

00:09:58.279 --> 00:09:59.080
Brother Chengwen,

00:09:59.480 --> 00:09:59.919
no matter

00:09:59.919 --> 00:10:01.639
what's going on between you and these girls,

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:03.080
let me confirm with you again.

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:04.879
The only person you want to marry and have kids with

00:10:04.879 --> 00:10:05.639
is me.

00:10:05.879 --> 00:10:06.840
Besides,

00:10:06.840 --> 00:10:08.720
I already told Grandpa I'm pregnant with your child.

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:10.039
You wouldn't want

00:10:10.039 --> 00:10:11.559
to become enemies with the Chen Family, right?

00:10:11.639 --> 00:10:12.440
What the heck?

00:10:13.639 --> 00:10:14.879
What is all this nonsense?

00:10:14.879 --> 00:10:15.679
No, wait.

00:10:15.960 --> 00:10:17.559
Her pregnancy is fake!

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:19.120
Wasn't that just to trick your grandpa? Darn it!

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:19.919
Shihan knows.

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:22.279
Mr. Lu,

00:10:22.639 --> 00:10:24.200
I only know

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.919
that I am the one who will always wait for you.

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:28.240
I...

00:10:32.360 --> 00:10:33.840
Can't I just sleep in the living room?

00:10:33.879 --> 00:10:34.360
No!

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:35.159
No!

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:52.919
You fate-defier.

00:10:52.919 --> 00:10:54.279
You're always, no matter where or when,

00:10:54.279 --> 00:10:55.320
causing trouble for me.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:56.960
Good thing I'm already used to it.

00:10:58.159 --> 00:10:59.759
What should I do about this?

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:01.840
We're still in a state of war right now.

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:03.960
The four of them insist I make a choice.

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:05.080
Who do I choose?

00:11:06.639 --> 00:11:07.200
Originally,

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:09.159
I wanted to wait until the reward settlement.

00:11:09.320 --> 00:11:10.840
Since the four of them are forcing you,

00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:11.759
as for the hidden reward,

00:11:11.759 --> 00:11:13.080
I'll tell you right now.

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:14.879
Hidden reward?

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:15.840
That's right.

00:11:15.879 --> 00:11:17.440
If you can survive until the end,

00:11:17.639 --> 00:11:19.360
the rewards aren't just money and medicine.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:19.879
Furthermore,

00:11:19.879 --> 00:11:21.480
you can choose one of them

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:22.559
to bring back to reality.

00:11:24.639 --> 00:11:25.440
What?

00:11:25.639 --> 00:11:27.639
Bring back to the real world?

00:11:28.159 --> 00:11:29.159
Are you serious?

00:11:29.639 --> 00:11:30.639
Think carefully about

00:11:30.840 --> 00:11:32.480
who you want to bring back the most.